.vscode/**
.vscode-test/**
src/**
.gitignore
.yarnrc
vsc-extension-quickstart.md
**/tsconfig.json
**/eslint.config.mjs
**/*.map
**/*.ts
**/.vscode-test.*
!parsers/*.wasm
# V2.1.2 scaffolds — the directory ships in the VSIX as the source of
# built-in project templates. The default rules above strip .ts files
# and tsconfig.json files; we re-include scaffolds/** so template
# contents survive packaging. Without this, scaffolded projects would
# be missing their source and configs.
!scaffolds/**
